snippet.title: WORTH LIFE Launch Trailer
snippet.description: Set in a "picture book world", WORTH LIFE is an action RPG and life sim. "With one million gold coins at your disposal, the possibilities are endless... start a business, invest in some land, or set off on an adventure." https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/worth-life-switch/ #switch #gaming #nintendoswitch
